## ğŸ“Œ Features  
âœ… **Fast & Parallel Scans** - Multi-threaded Nmap scans for efficiency.  
âœ… **Comprehensive Vulnerability Checks** - HTTP, SMB, FTP, SSH, RDP, DNS, SNMP, Redis, MongoDB, and more.  
